  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Thread the zucchini, bell peppers, onions, and mushrooms onto skewers.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the red curry paste, olive oil, salt, and pepper.",
    "Brush the curry paste mixture onto the vegetables.",
    "Roll the skewers in breadcrumbs to coat.",
    "Grill the skewers for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally.",
    "Serve the skewers on a wooden board.",
    "Garnish with fresh herbs, if desired."
